<bibRefCitation id="1B1D4B1A70D6FF30FBC2E9088F0EF8B0" author="Dalla Torre, C. G. de" box="[1062,1285,1885,1909]" pageId="168" pageNumber="169" refId="ref110399" refString="Dalla Torre, C. G. de (1893) Catalogus hymenopterorum hucusque descriptorum systematicus et synonymicus. Vol. 7 Formicidae (Heterogyna). Leipzig: G. Engelmann, 289 pp." type="book" year="1893">Dalla Torre (1893)</bibRefCitation>
