<bibRefCitation id="1B1D4B1A70D6FF30FED8E9D4880BF85C" author="Wheeler, W. M." box="[316,512,1921,1945]" pageId="168" pageNumber="169" pagination="1 - 142" refId="ref113081" refString="Wheeler, W. M. (1915 b) The ants of the Baltic Amber. Schriften der Physikalisch-okonomischen Gesellschaft zu Konigsberg in Pr., 55 (1914), 1 - 142." type="journal article" year="1915">Wheeler (1915b)</bibRefCitation>
